Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.93,0:03:03.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}However, no one has ever fully explored it
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:06.45,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,except for Gold Roger, King of the Pirates.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.49,0:03:12.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The New World has ruined\Nmany pirates' dreams and ambitions.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.49,0:03:17.40,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, Monkey D. Luffy, a boy whose body turned
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.40,0:03:20.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,to rubber after he ate the Gum-Gum Fruit,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.56,0:03:22.38,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and his friends venture into that sea.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.99,0:03:26.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna become the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.56,0:03:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.30,0:03:33.83,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To take down one of the Four Emperors -\Nthe rulers of the New World,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.83,0:03:36.87,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and the others formed a \Npirate alliance with Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.87,0:03:39.07,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,and have come to Dressrosa.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.79,0:03:42.94,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But caught up in the current \Nking Doflamingo's agenda,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:44.78,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,they were trapped along \Nwith the entire island.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.84,0:03:48.03,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Their allies have been bringing down
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.03,0:03:50.21,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,the executives of the Donquixote \NFamily one after another.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.95,0:03:53.37,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy and Law's fight against Doflamingo
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.37,0:03:57.60,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,at the Royal Palace is about \Nto come to a climax, too.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.23,0:04:01.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,This country has been taken over\Nby Doflamingo's trap.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.87,0:04:04.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whether we can restore it \Nto King Riku's hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.73,0:04:07.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...or we let it fall as a \Nhopeless country again...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.87,0:04:13.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our hope is in the hands of some pirates now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.11,0:04:15.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.49,0:04:17.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Lucy...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.40,0:04:26.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I respect that man!\NIf he at least recognizes how I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.41,0:04:28.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I can't ask for more!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.74,0:04:32.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't lie! You just have no choice!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.14,0:04:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're a man!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.81,0:04:41.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you know that much, shut up and fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.88,0:04:43.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll die for nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.57,0:04:50.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, I can't ask for more.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.29,0:04:55.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I'll be sent to kingdom come...{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.08,0:04:59.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}...by another man that I admire!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.90,0:05:02.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So long, Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:07.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Thank you for saying that I'm your friend!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.59,0:05:52.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.73,0:06:02.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The beast is roaring.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.10,0:06:06.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just come on up here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.70,0:06:12.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be surprised, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.83,0:06:20.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"Law Dies!\NLuffy's Raging Onslaught!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.21,0:06:26.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat has just taken down Bellamy...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.18,0:06:29.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That brings the number \Nof the tough enemies of
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.57,0:06:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the Donquixote Family down to two.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.06,0:06:36.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are only two left;
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.53,0:06:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,the top executive and the chief of staff, \NTrebol, and the boss of the Family,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.17,0:06:42.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Donquixote Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.36,0:06:46.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,As Roronoa Zoro said, \Nwe can't lower our guard
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.97,0:06:49.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,but the tide is turning for us in a big way!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.08,0:06:51.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Almost...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.39,0:06:54.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A little more to go and \Nthis nightmare will end!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.18,0:07:03.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.60,0:07:05.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's the matter, Viola-{\i1}sama{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.84,0:07:11.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Viola?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.10,0:07:15.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Our force has been reduced as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.15,0:07:16.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.36,0:07:19.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"Our force" means one of us got taken down?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.56,0:07:25.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who in the world could it be?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.11,0:07:29.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's Trafalgar Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.24,0:07:30.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.15,0:07:32.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can't believe it! Law-{\i1}dono{\i0}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.65,0:08:14.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure he'll be surprised, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.02,0:08:21.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When he sees your dead body...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.46,0:08:30.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,A FEW MINUTES AGO AT THE ROYAL PALACE
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:32.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sticky Launcher!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.74,0:08:41.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You better rest now, Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.23,0:08:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You must've learned enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.48,0:08:56.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The difference in our strengths \Nthat you can't make up no matter
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.41,0:08:57.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,what kind of cheap trick you play.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.33,0:09:01.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're no match even for me alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.80,0:09:04.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why would you want to \Nchallenge the two of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.09,0:09:15.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Straw Hat won't make it up here that easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.26,0:09:19.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If he had the nerve to beat up \Nhis "friend" right off the bat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.84,0:09:23.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,he could've saved you but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.27,0:09:29.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's such a naive idiot so...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.74,0:09:32.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's no use laying your hopes on him!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No use! No use!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.60,0:09:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're really a poor soul¬Å.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.86,0:09:40.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You were born in the hellish White Town...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.37,0:09:46.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In your youth, your future \Nseemed just plain darkness...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.09,0:09:51.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then you met my young brother,\NCorazon, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.89,0:09:55.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...he extended your life expectancy but...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.18,0:09:59.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...you've been holding a grudge against me\Nas if you're the ghost of him
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.84,0:10:03.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and living to get your revenge.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.64,0:10:05.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.60,0:10:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,For a man who is already dead, \Nyou've honed your skills,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.39,0:10:15.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,allied with Straw Hat, and \Neven come to Dressrosa...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.62,0:10:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an astounding obsession...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.75,0:10:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.66,0:10:22.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it's over now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.17,0:10:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What a worthless 13 years you've spent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.77,0:10:29.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I feel sorry for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.42,0:10:37.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your death is inevitable.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.24,0:10:39.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Die in vain like a dog!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.24,0:10:43.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,But, if you're gonna die anyway,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:50.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,wouldn't you rather make something out of it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.53,0:10:57.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's meaningful for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.73,0:11:04.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm only gonna say this once so listen carefully,\NTrafalgar D. Water Law.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.87,0:11:08.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Perform the Perpetual Youth Surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.87,0:11:12.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,which is the ultimate Op-Op \Ntechnique on me and...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.86,0:11:14.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.75,0:11:20.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,In exchange, I'll grant \Nyour wish, whatever it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.60,0:11:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.69,0:11:38.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.57,0:11:41.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.37,0:11:44.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you really mean it,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.95,0:11:50.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it is a good idea.\NIt's meaningful for both of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:55.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right. I'm in!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.71,0:12:04.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very understanding man!\NFinally, Doffy can have eternal life...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.45,0:12:05.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.31,0:12:09.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,bring Cora-{\i1}san{\i0} back to \Nlife for me, right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.55,0:12:16.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you finish with that,\Ngo lick all the butts of the people in this country!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.94,0:12:21.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No match for you?\NIt's no use laying my hopes?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.71,0:12:23.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.67,0:12:29.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's you who is not seeing \Nthe picture, Doflamingo!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.22,0:12:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Straw Hats have worked so \Nmany miracles up until today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.02,0:12:39.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take down Straw Hat-{\i1}ya{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:44.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You can't take back Caesar from him as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.86,0:12:50.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law! How could you say such a thing to Doffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.34,0:12:54.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's your future that's hanging by a hair...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.78,0:13:12.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What an idiot!\NYou never stop rebelling against me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.85,0:13:26.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The letters on your back... "Corazon"?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.97,0:13:28.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you aiming the satire at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.68,0:13:33.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,First of all, your pirate group \Nis called the Heart Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.54,0:13:35.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you aiming the satire at?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.96,0:13:39.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You don't even sit on the Heart seat
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.93,0:13:42.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,then why are you bearing \Nthe mark of the Heart?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.65,0:13:44.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.50,0:14:00.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How irritating!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.09,0:14:11.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Law... Corazon... This is it...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.37,0:14:19.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No one else will succeed \Nyour stupid obsession...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.70,0:14:29.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Your curse has been broken now!!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.30,0:14:34.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy died? You've got to be kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.40,0:14:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,After getting riddled by so \Nmany bullets, he can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.47,0:15:35.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,King Riku-{\i1}sama{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.69,0:15:38.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If we're in an unpredictable situation,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:43.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,it's even more necessary for us\Nto save the citizens who are in danger.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.96,0:15:46.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Yes, sir! Let's go!\N--I-I'll go, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.24,0:15:50.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'll go with you, too!\N--Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:52.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All right! Let's go down to the town now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.99,0:15:56.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not too late to minimize casualties!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.14,0:15:59.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Even though we can't fight,\Nthere are things we can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.54,0:16:01.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.85,0:16:22.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doffy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.30,0:16:32.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Well, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.83,0:16:36.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can get hold of the Op-Op Fruit again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.14,0:16:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.76,0:16:43.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, all there is left to do is...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.10,0:16:48.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Take care...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.35,0:16:52.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.15,0:17:38.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Doflamingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.50,0:17:45.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.48,0:17:56.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're late, Straw Hat.\NSince I emancipated him,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.35,0:18:01.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Bellamy became free, didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.49,0:18:04.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't play dumb! You knew full well!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.06,0:18:14.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That he wasn't gonna run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.45,0:18:16.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.96,0:18:18.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Elephant Gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:22.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Spiderweb!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.95,0:18:29.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I see. So Bellamy didn't run away.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.63,0:18:34.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's so funny?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.33,0:18:42.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.60,0:18:45.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Hawk Gatling!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.37,0:19:19.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Break White!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.91,0:19:25.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:38.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Tra-guy!\NWhy are you bleeding so much?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.09,0:19:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to your arm?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.78,0:19:41.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.61,0:19:44.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stay with me! Tra-guy! Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.68,0:19:45.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Tra-guy!!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.73,0:19:54.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's dead... It's obvious.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.27,0:19:56.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You're lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.53,0:20:02.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not. It seemed like he trusted \Nyou so much but what a shame.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.70,0:20:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He said you can work miracles.\NCan you, Straw Hat?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.98,0:20:14.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you were that strong\Nwhen I fought you, though...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.69,0:20:18.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Now, bring it on! There are the two of us!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.86,0:20:21.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How dare you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:25.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.74,0:20:27.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pentachromatic Strings!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.10,0:20:30.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Battle-Axe!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.36,0:20:44.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:47.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Giant Whip!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.26,0:20:48.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Armament Hardening!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.58,0:20:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What the hell is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.46,0:21:03.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Gum-Gum...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.57,0:21:07.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...Spring Bullet!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.83,0:21:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You almost got me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.27,0:21:55.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.54,0:21:57.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.07,0:22:13.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Stay where you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.68,0:22:14.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.38,0:22:28.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I hear something.\N--Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.43,0:22:29.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.68,0:22:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.23,0:22:40.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it was just my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:42.56,0:22:44.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, it is moving!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.20,0:22:49.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Oh, please...\N--The wall of strings is...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.33,0:22:55.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Shrinking!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.38,0:23:04.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'll let you follow Law in death shortly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.80,0:23:10.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Let's bring an end to this game.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.12,0:23:13.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Mingo!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.22,0:23:14.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--{\i1}Wait.{\i0}\N--What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.44,0:23:18.27,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Listen carefully, Straw Hat-ya.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.32,0:23:28.17,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Doflamingo's cold-blooded extermination \Nplan is finally put in motion!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.20,0:23:33.30,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The shrinking wall of strings cuts up Dressrosa!\NThere is only one hour left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.66,0:23:36.14,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When it seems like every \Nhope has been dashed,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.14,0:23:40.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,a tenacious attack that takes a \None-and-only chance, rings out!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.19,0:23:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.57,0:23:44.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,"A Blade of Tenacity! The \NGamma Knife Counterattack!"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.34,0:23:46.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.38,0:23:49.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.38,0:23:51.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,
